description: Lucky Minerals Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and evaluation of mineral properties. The company explores for gold, copper, and molybdenum deposits. It holds a 100% interest in the Fortuna project comprises 12 contiguous mining concessions covering approximately 55,000 hectares in a prolific mineralized zone in southern Ecuador. Lucky Minerals Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. M. Francois Perron BSc, MBA
